{"tag":"section","attrib":{"id":"idbac9c7e1-3a70-11f1-ae07-e4213316b5fa","identifier":"/us/usc/t42/s1436b"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"1436b"},"text":"§ 1436b.","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":" Financial assistance in impacted areas","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"content","attrib":{},"text":"\n","children":[{"tag":"p","attrib":{},"text":"The Secretary of Housing and Urban Development shall not exclude from consideration for financial assistance under federally assisted housing programs proposals for housing projects solely because the site proposed is located within an impacted area. For the purposes of this section, the term “federally assisted housing programs” means any program authorized by the United States Housing Act of 1937 [","children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/usc/t42/s1437"},"text":"42 U.S.C. 1437","children":[],"tail":" et seq.], sections 1715z and 1715z–1 of title 12, section 101 of the Housing and Urban Development Act of 1965 ["},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/usc/t12/s1701s"},"text":"12 U.S.C. 1701s","children":[],"tail":"], or "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/usc/t12/s1701q"},"text":"section 1701q of title 12","children":[],"tail":"."}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":null},{"tag":"sourceCredit","attrib":{"id":"idbac9c7e2-3a70-11f1-ae07-e4213316b5fa"},"text":"(","children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/96/399/tII/s216"},"text":"Pub. L. 96–399, title II, § 216","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"date","attrib":{"date":"1980-10-08"},"text":"Oct. 8, 1980","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/stat/94/1638"},"text":"94 Stat. 1638","children":[],"tail":".)"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"notes","attrib":{"type":"uscNote","id":"idbac9c7e3-3a70-11f1-ae07-e4213316b5fa"},"text":"\n","children":[{"tag":"note","attrib":{"role":"crossHeading","topic":"editorialNotes","id":"idbac9c7e4-3a70-11f1-ae07-e4213316b5fa"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"b","attrib":{},"text":"Editorial Notes","children":[],"tail":null}],"tail":null}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"note","attrib":{"topic":"referencesInText","id":"idbac9c7e5-3a70-11f1-ae07-e4213316b5fa"},"text":"\n","children":[{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":"References in Text","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"p","attrib":{},"text":"The United States Housing Act of 1937, referred to in text, is ","children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/act/1937-09-01/ch896"},"text":"act Sept. 1, 1937, ch. 896","children":[],"tail":", as revised generally by "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/93/383/tII/s201/a"},"text":"Pub. L. 93–383, title II, § 201(a)","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"date","attrib":{"date":"1974-08-22"},"text":"Aug. 22, 1974","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/stat/88/653"},"text":"88 Stat. 653","children":[],"tail":", which is classified generally to this chapter (§ 1437 et seq.). For complete classification of this Act to the Code, see Short Title note set out under "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/usc/t42/s1437"},"text":"section 1437 of this title","children":[],"tail":" and Tables."}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"p","attrib":{},"text":"Section 101 of the Housing and Urban Development Act of 1965, referred to in text, is ","children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/89/117/s101"},"text":"section 101 of Pub. L. 89–117","children":[],"tail":", title I, "},{"tag":"date","attrib":{"date":"1965-08-10"},"text":"Aug. 10, 1965","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/stat/79/451"},"text":"79 Stat. 451","children":[],"tail":", which enacted "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/usc/t12/s1701s"},"text":"section 1701s of Title 12","children":[],"tail":", Banks and Banking, and amended sections 1451 and 1465 of this title."}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"note","attrib":{"topic":"codification","id":"idbac9c7e6-3a70-11f1-ae07-e4213316b5fa"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":"Codification","children":[],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"p","attrib":{},"text":"Section was enacted as part of the Housing and Community Development Act of 1980, and not as part of the United States Housing Act of 1937 which comprises this chapter.","children":[],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":null}
